  "text": "TiO 2 NP is a commercial product (Sigma-Aldrich, CAS No. 13463-67-7). Characteristic measurement and cell treatment were performed according to a previous study [CITATION_1] . Briefly, TiO 2 NPs were dispersed in the complete cell culture medium, vortexed at high speed, and sonicated for 30 min (100 W) before characteristic measurement. Stock solution (1 mg/ml) was gradually diluted and sonicated for another cycle before being administrated to cells.",
